      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry — exact COU device. Operating envelope partially covered (3/5 points). Long-term hemolysis accumulation under pulsatile VAD loading not validated; only steady-state conditions tested. Achieved Gradation 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
