      "rationale": "Single turbulence model (SST k-omega) and single hemolysis power-law model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) used throughout. No multi-model comparison performed. Model form uncertainty is the dominant uncharacterized source at MRL 5. Not assessed; critical gap for absolute hemolysis prediction.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/orphan-synthesis-node-001"
